Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:29.67,Default,Kot,0,0,0,,{\blur0}Vì thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:34.46,Default,Kot,0,0,0,,{\blur0}Ba... Mẹ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.92,Default,Kot,0,0,0,,{\blur0}Mừng ba mẹ đã về.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:49.77,Default,Oka,0,0,0,,{\blur0\i1}Chiếc cặp ấy đã chu du khắp thế giới.
