Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:55.73,Default,Oka,0,0,0,,{\blur0\i1}đảo băng,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.78,Default,Oka,0,0,0,,{\blur0\i1}núi cao,
